⚙️ HYBRID BUILD SYSTEM
Use:
Node.js & pnpm
Java (OpenJDK 21)
Gradle 8.8
Android SDK (Target 35)
Capacitor bridge
Build Process:
pnpm build → generate /dist
npx cap sync → move files to Android
./gradlew assembleDebug → build APK
Concept Explanation:
Hybrid App = Android frame
Web App = UI inside
Capacitor = bridge
Bundle assets:
HTML, CSS, JS stored inside APK
Faster load, partial offline support
